      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Hamburg, ¶  ¶ 11 March ¶  ¶ 1853 ¶  ¶ Most esteemed Professor, ¶  ¶ The ¶  ¶ dispatch of the manuscript ¶  ¶ has ¶  ¶ been delayed by various impediments, ¶  ¶ and ¶  ¶ I also found some things to imp...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M53.03.11</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Wilhelm Sonder to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText" style="hyphenate: false; " xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Number MS not seen; extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>14.</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
               </note>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Hamburg d. 11 März 53</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Geehrtester Herr Professor!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die Absendung des Manuskriptes ist durch mancherlei Abhaltungen verzögert worden, auch fand ich noch einiges zu verbessern, nachdem ich die letzten Hefte der Icones plantarum Hook. erhielt. Es soll mich freuen, wenn durch diese Verzögerung der<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Druck nicht aufgehalten wird. Müller schreibt mir neulich, ich möge ihm bald Abdrucke zukommen lassen, er hoffe dadurch Unterstützung bei der Regierung zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>finden. Möchten Sie nicht die<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Gefälligkeit haben, mir mit der Post alle oder doch wenigstens 4 – 5 Abdrucke von Müllers Diagnos.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>etc zu schicken? Ich möchte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ihm gerne mit dem, Ende dieses Monats abgehenden Dampfschiffe einige übersenden u die anderen mit einem Segelschiffe.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Von dem beifolgenden Manuskripte möchte ich auch gerne 12 – 15 Abdrucke erhalten, um nicht allein Dr. Müller, sondern auch den anderen Mitarbeitern an<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>der Enumeratio davon abgeben zu können.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich werde mich jetzt daran machen, die Algenbestimmungen zusammen zu schreiben,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>bis dahin wird Prof. Braun mit den<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Characeen auch fertig sein. Werden Sie denn nicht wenigstens das Referat über die Sapindaceen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>übernehmen? Vielleicht auch<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>noch über einige andere kleine<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>auch oder grössere Familien? Aus den Compositeen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ersehen Sie,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>dass Müller’s Sammlung in vieler Hinsicht der von Preiss nicht nachsteht.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Hochachtungsvoll<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ergebener<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Hamburg,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>11 March<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1853<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Most esteemed Professor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>dispatch of the manuscript<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>been delayed by various impediments,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I also found some things to improve after I received the last<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>numbers<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Icones plantarum</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Hooker. I should be pleased if the printing is not<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>held up by this delay. Mueller<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>wrote<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>me<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>recently<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that I should have him reprints sent to him soon, as he hoped to find support<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with the government<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>them.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Would you not have the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>courtesy to send me by post<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>all<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>or at least 4 - 5 copies<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of Mueller's diagnoses<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>etc? I would like to send<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>him some<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the steamship leaving at the end of this month and the others<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a sailing ship.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I would also like to receive 12 - 15<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>reprints<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of the enclosed manuscript, in order to be able<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to give them not only to Dr. Mueller, but also to the other collaborators on the Enmeratio.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I will now start to write the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>algal determinations together,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by then Prof. Braun will also be finished with the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Characeae.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Will you then not at least take on the report<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on the Sapindaceae? Perhaps also on some other small<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>or<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>also larger families? From the Compositae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>you will see that Mueller's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>collection is in many respects not inferior to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Preiss.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
         </div>
      </body>
